      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a pretty intense way to put it. You said it's \"forcing students\" to use certain lenses and that it's a \"departure from consensus\"—does that mean the stuff being taught now is actually inaccurate, or is it just a different way of looking at the same facts?",
